metadata.name: Survivors
metadata.description:
Exactly where we humans are immersed in our own lives, where we all see the end of this life cycle far away, we are trapped in the infinity that we have created in our limited minds, and the daily life of all of us has taken over.
We are all doomed to repeat the past because we have not learned from history .
Civilizations came and went ... but when does this cycle change?

resolution: 2160*2700
time: 10 seconds loop
